title: Empire Strikes Back for PSP
description:
Star Wars Episode V: The Empire Strikes Back, for PSP viewing. Ripped from DVD
and converted using iPSP. Excellent video and sound reproduction, fits on a 512mb Memory Stick and leaves space for game saves and other data.

The correct folder name for videos is E:MP_ROOT100MNV01 (where E: is the drive 
letter of your PSP). Put both of these files in 100MNV01 folder.
